                     ንወጥን፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘይነግር፡ ኍልቍ፡ ዓመታተ፡ ዓለም፡
                     ዘአስተጋብአ፡ አብ፡ ክቡር፡ ወትሩፍ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወልደ፡ አሚድ፡  ዘብሔረ፡ 
                        ግብጽ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ተሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ አሜን፡</dcterms:hasPart><crm:P57_has_number_of_parts rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">0</crm:P57_has_number_of_parts><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="BDLbruce92/colophon/coloph1"/><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/><betmas:locusTo/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>2009</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4711Giyorgis"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2916Bruce"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLbruce92/colophon/coloph1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Colophon"/><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusTarget/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>2009</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2916Bruce"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLbruce92/msitem/ms_i4"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont"/><dcterms:hasPart>Chronology of the Ethiopian kings from Yǝkunno ʾAmlāk to Yoḥannǝs I
